@startuml
title Logging Policy

start

:Wake every 1 second;
:Read BME280 and DS1306;
:Update display every wake cycle;

if (logging enabled?) then (yes)
  if (log interval elapsed?) then (yes)
    :Append record to RAM buffer;
    if (RAM buffer full?) then (yes)
      :Send block to Flash Writer Task;
    else (no)
    endif
  else (no)
  endif
else (no)
endif

:Enter light sleep for 1 second;
stop

@enduml
